  note    = {Applied MAGMA cell-type enrichment to schizophrenia GWAS (PGC2: 40,675 cases) using Linnarsson mouse brain snRNA-seq atlas (9,970 cells). Schizophrenia signal enriched in pyramidal neurons (CA1, subiculum), medium spiny neurons (striatum), somatostatin-positive interneurons. Published analysis pipeline via R package MAGMA_celltyping. Level 1 taxonomy (~70 cell types) used by mecfsscience.org analysis. Consistent across 7 independent cell-type datasets},
